content: Hello! Welcome to my site. I’m Waleed—AI/ML engineer and full-stack developer. How can I help you today?

- RAG-based Chatbot with LLM and ReactJs: I built a chatbot using Retrieval-Augmented Generation with large language models integrated into a React frontend.

- Ritual Generator Web App: A web app generating personalized rituals.
- AI-RiceHarbor App: This was my final year project, focusing on AI applications related to rice farming.

These projects reflect my passion for creating practical AI solutions from end to end. If you'd like details on any of these, just let me know!
